杀手乐队凭借《布莱特赛德先生》荣获两项吉尼斯世界纪录https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-presented-with-two-guinness-world-records-for-mr-brightside-3773956?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-killers-presented-布莱赛德先生创下两项吉尼斯世界纪录Elizabeth AubreyThu, 11 Jul 2024 11:16:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3773956 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 O2 杀手乐队的布兰登·弗劳尔斯 (Brandon Flowers)" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>主唱布兰登·弗劳尔斯 (Brandon Flowers) 表示：“我们只是乐此不疲”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-presented-with-two-guinness-world-records-for-mr-brightside-3773956">The Killers 凭借《Brightside 先生》荣获两项吉尼斯世界纪录的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 O2 杀手乐队的布兰登·弗劳尔斯 (Brandon Flowers)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Brandon-Flowers-of-The-Killers-CREDIT_-Chris-Phelps_Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">杀手乐队</a>凭借其热门歌曲“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gGdGFtwCNBE&amp;amp;embeds_referring_euri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2F&amp;amp;source_ve_path=MjM4NTE">Mr Brightside</a> ”荣获两项吉尼斯世界纪录。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-killers-live-in-london-rebel-diamonds-setlist-photos-review-3772814">杀手乐队在伦敦演出：令人眼花缭乱的深切和令人惊讶的擦除外观</a></strong></li></ul><p>截至 7 月 4 日，该曲目在英国单曲榜上停留时间总计 416 周，是组合中最长的，也是单曲在英国单曲榜上停留时间最长的周数。总共将近八年。</p><p> 《Mr Brightside》是乐队<i>Hot Fuss</i>的首张单曲，于 2003 年 9 月首次发行，并于 2004 年重新发行。</p><p>乐队在向<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2024/7/the-killers-reveal-why-theyll-never-get-sick-of-performing-record-breaking-mr-brightside?utm_campaign=feed&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=later-linkinbio" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>吉尼斯世界纪录</em></a>讲述这一成就时表示，他们永远不会厌倦演奏这首歌。</p><p>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandon-flowers">布兰登·弗劳尔斯 (Brandon Flowers)</a>告诉他们：“这对我们来说仍然具有感染力，我知道有些人无法理解它，但你会看到反应（当你现场观看时）。</p><p> “很难不被它感动或不为它兴奋，今晚会有人从未看过它的现场表演，有些人已经看过 45 次了。我们就是不会厌倦。”</p><p>鼓手 Ronnie Vannucci Jr. 补充道：“我们开始演奏，然后我们享受这段旅程，然后我们中的一个人必须停止它，这是其中一首歌曲。</p><p> “这是一种高度互惠的事情，我们和他们一样享受这段旅程。”</p><p>吉他手戴夫·科宁 (Dave Keuning) 补充道：“我认为这是我们想象出来的，但在我们开始整个事情之前，你永远不会知道。没有任何保证。”</p><p>谈及这一具有里程碑意义的成就时，吉尼斯世界纪录评审员威尔·芒福德 (Will Munford) 表示：“自 2000 年代中期以来，《布莱特塞德先生》已经占据了无数舞池，并为许多深夜合唱做出了贡献。</p><p> “我们很荣幸为杀手乐队授予这首歌两项吉尼斯世界纪录称号，这证明了这首歌能够受到几代人的喜爱，并作为历史经典之一经受住时间的考验。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9P3PAjtlsI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.